reviewText: Amazing, real deal, thank you, A+
I haven't watched it yet, but it kept a 7, 5, and 2 year old entertained for an entire weekend while their Mommy wasn't feeling good.
DOUBLE FEATURE FOR EVERY GOOSEBUMPS FAN. KIDS AND ADULTS WILL LIKE THE STORY LINES IN BOTH OF THESE MOVIES FROM THE POPULAR 90'S SERIES.
Goosebumps:  Ghost next door / shocker on shock street.  My son really like it.  Just right for a ten year old.
I enjoy watching Goosebumps with my boys ages 7 and 4, we have a blast and this is a fun dvd.
My 7 year old daughter loves Goosebumps books and videos. They're not too scary for her and they're well made. They remind me of the Twilight Zone series I used to watch when I was younger.
